Class ArrayRestore

All Implemented Interfaces:
TrailElement
public class ArrayRestore
extends Restore

This TrailElement is the counterpiece for the xastore instructions. It is generated when an array is changed. This can only happen when one of the following instructions is executed: aastore, bastore, castore, dastore, fastore, iastore, lastore, sastore. It takes the information which index of what arrayref has to be restored, and what its original value was.

1.0.0, 2008-11-24
